title: Bikewatching
description: A project where I analyzed bike rental data in New York City to identify trends and patterns in bike usage.

title: ECOMENU: Low Carbon Recipe Recommender
description: A hackathon project where I developed a recipe recommendation platform based on sustainability data.

title: San Diego Crime Analysis
description: I cleaned and analyzed data from San Diego Police Department to identify trends that are present in San Diego crimes over the past 4 years.

title: Starry Sticker Shop Analysis
description: Analyzed business data for my own sticker shop, helping to optimize pricing and product selection.
